<shopify_specifics>
## Shopify-Specific Context

### Package Distribution
- **@shopify-internal/slack-mcp@latest** (CURRENT): Served from Shopify's internal npm registry
  - **Authentication**: Requires Shopify dev tool installed (for npm registry access)
  - **No GitHub auth needed**: Direct from internal registry
  - **Prerequisite**: `dev` tool must be configured (see https://technical-learning.docs.shopify.io/setup/dev)
- **github:shopify-playground/slack-mcp** (LEGACY): Served from GitHub, requires PAT with SSO authorization
  - **Shopify org**: Main organization for internal repos
  - **shopify-playground org**: Where legacy package is hosted
  - **Access method**: Request via Okta (https://shopify.okta.com/)
  - **Typical approval**: Automatic for Shopify employees

### Slack Workspace & Authentication
- **Workspace**: shopify.slack.com
- **Authentication Methods**:
  - **RECOMMENDED**: Automated interactive auth (new default - server guides user through setup)
  - **FALLBACK**: Manual token extraction via Chrome DevTools
- **Authentication**: @shopify.com email + 2FA
- **Token format** (manual method only): Must use session tokens (xoxc-) and cookies (xoxd-)
- **Token lifespan**: Session-based tokens that expire when you logout/login or after period of inactivity (can be 15-30 minutes to several weeks depending on session activity)
- **Cookie encoding** (manual method only): CRITICAL - Must keep cookie URL-encoded (do NOT decode %2F, %2B, %3D, etc.)

### Development Environment
- **Node.js**: Must be installed via NVM (not Homebrew)
- **Shell**: Typically zsh on macOS (check ~/.zshrc and ~/.zprofile)
- **PATH**: Cursor reads from shell profile, requires restart after PATH changes
- **Browser**: Chrome required for Slack token extraction

### Known Working Versions
- Node: v20.11.0 (v20.x LTS recommended)
- npm: 10.2.4
- OS: Any (macOS, Windows, Linux)
- @shopify-internal/slack-mcp: latest (1.0.0+)
- Chrome browser: Required for manual token extraction fallback only (automated auth doesn't need it)
- Shopify dev tool: Required for npm registry access
</shopify_specifics>

